{
  "version": "Notebook/1.0",
  "items": [
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "## 🛡️ Third-Party Application Vulnerabilities\n\nA single pane for **DevSecOps remediation planning** across two domains:\n\n1. **🔐 Entra ID Applications** — third-party & in-house **app registrations / enterprise apps** scored for risky permissions, credential hygiene, risky OAuth consents, and **Microsoft Entra recommendations** (with *addressed / not-addressed* status and remediation guidance). Powered by **Microsoft Graph**.\n2. **💿 Software Vulnerabilities (Defender)** — non-Microsoft **software CVEs** discovered by **Microsoft Defender Vulnerability Management (MDVM)** via Azure Resource Graph (`securityresources`).\n\n> Use the **domain selector** below to switch between the two views."
      },
      "name": "title"
    },
    {
      "type": 9,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "id": "param-subscriptions",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "Subscriptions",
            "label": "Subscriptions",
            "type": 6,
            "isRequired": true,
            "multiSelect": true,
            "quote": "'",
            "delimiter": ",",
            "typeSettings": {
              "additionalResourceOptions": [
                "value::all"
              ],
              "includeAll": true
            },
            "value": [
              "value::all"
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "param-severity",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "Severity",
            "label": "Severity",
            "type": 2,
            "multiSelect": true,
            "quote": "'",
            "delimiter": ",",
            "typeSettings": {
              "additionalResourceOptions": [
                "value::all"
              ]
            },
            "jsonData": "[\r\n {\"value\":\"Critical\",\"label\":\"Critical\",\"selected\":true},\r\n {\"value\":\"High\",\"label\":\"High\",\"selected\":true},\r\n {\"value\":\"Medium\",\"label\":\"Medium\"},\r\n {\"value\":\"Low\",\"label\":\"Low\"}\r\n]",
            "value": [
              "value::all"
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "param-vendor",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "Vendor",
            "label": "Vendor",
            "type": 2,
            "multiSelect": true,
            "quote": "'",
            "delimiter": ",",
            "query": "securityresources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.security/assessments/subassessments'\r\n| where isnotempty(properties.additionalData.softwareName) or isnotempty(properties.additionalData.vendor)\r\n| extend vendor = tostring(coalesce(properties.additionalData.vendor, 'Unknown'))\r\n| where tolower(vendor) !contains 'microsoft'\r\n| distinct vendor\r\n| order by vendor asc",
            "crossComponentResources": [
              "{Subscriptions}"
            ],
            "queryType": 10,
            "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
            "typeSettings": {
              "additionalResourceOptions": [
                "value::all"
              ],
              "showDefault": false
            },
            "value": [
              "value::all"
            ]
          }
        ],
        "style": "pills",
        "queryType": 10,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources"
      },
      "name": "parameters"
    },
