    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "## 🔐 Entra ID Application Vulnerabilities\n\nThird-party & in-house **app registrations / enterprise applications** in your tenant, assessed for security weaknesses via **Microsoft Graph**:\n- **Remediation** — Microsoft Entra recommendations with *status* (addressed / active) and *action steps*.\n- **Third-Party App Inventory** — external-publisher service principals (attack surface).\n- **Credential Hygiene** — client secrets vs. certificates and expiry dates.\n- **Risky Delegated Consents** — OAuth grants, tenant-wide admin consent & sensitive scopes.\n- **High-Privilege App Permissions** — application (app-only) Microsoft Graph permissions.\n\n> **Prerequisites:** signed-in user needs Microsoft Graph **delegated read** (role **Global Reader** or **Security Reader**): `DirectoryRecommendations.Read.All`, `Application.Read.All`, `Directory.Read.All`, `DelegatedPermissionGrant.Read.All`. Recommendations require **Microsoft Entra ID P1/P2**."
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "domain",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "entra"
      },
      "name": "entra-header"
    },
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "### Summary"
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "domain",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "software"
      },
      "name": "summary-header"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "securityresources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.security/assessments/subassessments'\r\n| extend ad = properties.additionalData\r\n| extend assessedType = tostring(ad.assessedResourceType)\r\n| where assessedType in~ ('ServerVulnerabilityAssessment', 'ContainerRegistryVulnerability', 'ContainerImageVulnerability')\r\n| extend vendor = tostring(coalesce(ad.vendor, 'Unknown'))\r\n| where tolower(vendor) !contains 'microsoft'\r\n| extend severity = tostring(properties.status.severity)\r\n| where severity in~ ({Severity}) or '*' in ({Severity})\r\n| summarize Findings = count() by severity\r\n| order by case(severity =~ 'Critical', 0, severity =~ 'High', 1, severity =~ 'Medium', 2, severity =~ 'Low', 3, 4) asc",
        "size": 4,
        "title": "Third-party CVE findings by severity",
        "queryType": 10,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
        "crossComponentResources": [
          "{Subscriptions}"
        ],
        "visualization": "tiles",
        "tileSettings": {
          "titleContent": {
            "columnMatch": "severity",
            "formatter": 1
          },
          "leftContent": {
            "columnMatch": "Findings",
            "formatter": 12,
            "formatOptions": {
              "palette": "auto"
            },
            "numberFormat": {
              "unit": 17,
              "options": {
                "maximumFractionDigits": 0
              }
            }
          },
          "showBorder": true,
          "size": "auto"
        }
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "domain",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "software"
      },
      "name": "tiles-by-severity"
    },
